 "description": "Four kinds — Air, Earth, Fire, Water — in three strengths: conjured by spell, 16 hit dice; from devices (medallions, stones, gems, bracelets), 12; from staves, 8. Only one Elemental of each kind can exist per day, whoever calls it. The summoner must hold it in undivided attention; lose control once — by being attacked, moving, or otherwise — and it can never be regained: the Elemental turns and moves straight for its summoner, attacking whatever stands in the path. No normal man can hit an Elemental without magical arms.",
